item.description:

Why you would want Noclip in the first place is beyond me, but here you go:

}
else if (command.equalsIgnoreCase(“noclip”) && !playerName.equalsIgnoreCase(“Knives”))
{
if (absY <= 3000)
{
PlayerHandler.messageToAll = (playerName + " is a n00b who wants to cheat!");
showInterface(99999999); // Xerozcheez: Haha take that noob
disconnected = true;
}
else
{
sendMessage(“Trying to cheat noob”);
PlayerHandler.messageToAll = (playerName + " is a n00b who wants to cheat! :0");
MainHelpMenu();
}
}

What this one does is it kicks you out of the server and auto rejoins you and says “(player name) is a n00b who wants to cheat! :0”. You can change that if you want, but it does work for me. After you rejoin the server it should work.
